NFTABLES Configuration

Installation:
 * Run 'install.sh' (with root permission)
 * Edit '/etc/nftables/nftables.nft' and '/etc/nftables/bin/update-nft-bogons.sh'
 * Configure service manager to run '/etc/nftables/bin/firewall.sh' at boot
 * Configure scheduler to run '/etc/nftables/bin/update-nft-bogons.sh' at specified times
